The homepage should act as a gateway to three worlds:
- writing
- research
- fandom

Architecture rules:
- present a unified identity first
- do not split the homepage into three unrelated mini-sites
- each section should feel like a facet of the same person
- every page should have a clear primary action or next step
- list pages should support scanning
- detail pages should support immersion

When building a page, decide whether it is:
- list-first
- reading-first
- gallery-first
- evidence-first

Then optimize layout accordingly.
